imdb.plot outline: Meet Dave (Played by Blake Suarez), an average Joe just trying to do the right thing. Introduce his childhood best friend and bumbling sidekick, Al (Derek Huey) and disaster is sure to ensue! Add to the mix a pair of zany cops and top it off with a down on his luck villain (Comedian Eddie B) and you end up with quite a "Strange Day!" A colorful cast, Dan Braverman as "Johnny Cockring", Jemma Evans as Mrs. Rogers, Veteran Police Officer Rogers (John Dalbosco) and his rookie sidekick Officer Gingers (Drew Brown).
